'''磨西镇'''位于[[中国|中国]][[四川省|四川省]][[甘孜州|甘孜州]][[泸定县|泸定县]]中部，[[贡嘎山|贡嘎山]]东麓，海拔约1600米。“磨西”为古羌语，意为“宝地”<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 新浪 | title = 探访遥远的风情小镇 磨西镇 | url = http://sc.sina.com.cn/life/travel/ts/2010-01-13/10199940.html | date = 2010-01-13 | accessdate = 2011-09-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101123/http://sc.sina.com.cn/life/travel/ts/2010-01-13/10199940.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

磨西镇属于海螺沟景区管理局管理，是进入[[海螺沟|海螺沟]]的旅游接待基地和入口。距[[成都|成都]]约304公里，距[[泸定|泸定]]县城52公里，距[[康定市|康定]]约70公里<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 人民网 | title = 磨西镇：川藏通道上的繁华重镇 | url = http://travel.people.com.cn/GB/41636/41637/65187/65201/4474165.html | date = 2006-06-14 | accessdate = 2011-09-19 | archive-date = 2009-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091016101018/http://travel.people.com.cn/GB/41636/41637/65187/65201/4474165.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。


